              spiritual benefits and rituals.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                <img
                  src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544367567-0f2fcb009e0b?w=100"
                  alt="Author"
                  class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full object-cover"
                />
                <span class="text-sm text-brand-gray">Radha Devi</span>
              </div>
              <a
                href="#"
                class="text-secondary font-semibold text-sm hover:text-secondary-hover transition flex items-center"
              >
                Read More <span class="material-icons text-sm ml-1"
                  >arrow_forward</span
